                      00055 ;bit 7 ADFM: A/D Result Format Select bit
                      00056 ;1 = Right justified. 6 Most Significant bits of ADRESH are read as ‘0’.
                      00057 ;0 = Left justified. 6 Least Significant bits of ADRESL are read as ‘0’.
